# AutoFlow Project Rules

## Git Commit Messages
All commit messages must strictly follow this prefix structure:
- Features/Additions: `[ADD] : <message>`  (do not use `feat:`)
- Fixes/Corrections: `[FIX] : <message>` (do not use `fix:`)

Example:
`[ADD] : start command and rich terminal UI`
`[FIX] : uniform hexagon logo and update copyright`
